    <p>
      
      In the situation where a rational function is undefined at a point but does not have a vertical asymptote there, we'll say that the graph of the function has a <term>hole</term>.  <idx><h>rational function</h><h>hole</h></idx> 
    </p>

    <definition xml:id="def-rf-hole">
